{"tid":1433601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港機場消遣好去處","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:11:08.000Z","uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"275af3458b8f382f9444f5b010726e7bc2f7c8cb","tid":1433601,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"機場，一個讓人又愛又恨的地方。這裏是出國旅行、通往度假天堂的必經之地，可是碰上倒霉的日子，錯過航班、班機延誤，或是不小心早到了三小時&hellip;&hellip;種種狀況讓你滯留此地，不禁會覺得度日如年。不過在香港國際機場，你絕對不會覺得等待的時間難熬，因為這裏有一系列的消閒娛樂好去處，免稅店、餐廳、休息室、室內體育館，統統一應俱全，難怪赤鱲角機場長期高踞全球最佳機場的前列！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/103968283/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F103968283%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=5a58c28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港機場好去處<br />\n UA IMAX @ Airport<br />\n戲院, IMAX<br />\n機場 UA IMAX 影院<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\n既然有數小時的空檔，何不看一齣電影，感受 IMAX 的威力？機場戲院的位置距離市區有點遠，不多人會進場看戲，所以通常都可以選擇心水座位。這裏擁有全港最大的 IMAX 巨型銀幕，多聲道數碼環繞音響系統配合幾何設計，不少戲迷都會專程來體驗最棒的視聽享受！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/105384691/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F105384691%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=211ab882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n BITE&amp;BITE with LINE FRIENDS<br />\n餐廳<br />\nBite &amp; Bite with Line Friends<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\n提供多款韓式及西式美食，更是世界上唯一讓大家可以一邊與眾多 Line Friends 朋友仔一齊欣賞機場靚景，一邊享用美食，一邊舒服地等候上機的地方。餐廳內設有大量打卡位，包括遙望停機坪的 Brown 、帶廚師帽的 Sally 、為大家送餐做好準備的 Cony、準備好舉杯與大家自拍的 Choco 等等，讓大家無限打卡。菜單方面結合了韓式和西式兩種截然不同的風味，以滿足世界各地顧客的口味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/105395456/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F105395456%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=df8b9ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 瑜逸閣 the sanctuary by pure yoga @hk airport<br />\n運動健身<br />\n瑜逸閣<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\n瑜伽運動有益身心，隨地隨地也能進行，連在上飛機前也可以做。國泰航空與瑜珈中心 Pure Yoga 合作，在玉衡堂商務貴賓室開設瑜逸閣，為乘客提供放鬆身心的寧靜空間。大家可以跟着 Pure Yoga 導師的教學影片做瑜伽，，或者在專用座椅上，聆聽 Pure Yoga 導師的冥想引導。只要你是國泰航空的頭等及商務客艙旅客、特選馬可孛羅會會員和「寰宇一家」 飛行常客，都能到這裏動動筋骨舒壓！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/103968925/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F103968925%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=4f959d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Aviation Discovery Centre<br />\n博物館, 交通<br />\n航空探知館<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\n飛機迷如果出國旅遊，上機前不妨去航空探知館，探索迷人的飛機世界。航空探知館免費開放，設有多個趣味互動展品、飛機駕駛艙模型、香港航空發展史介紹。館內更有模擬駕駛艙，讓你一嘗駕駛飛機的滋味，需要另外收費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/103968993/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F103968993%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=4b38bdcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n GreenLive Air<br />\n好去處, 體育活動<br />\nGreenLive Air<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\n下次等上機時，何不善用空檔，打一場高爾夫球？沒有說笑，到機場裏的室內高爾夫球俱樂部 GreenLive Air ，大家可以玩九洞及18洞遊戲模擬高球遊戲，盡情練習推桿和開球技巧。無論天氣好壞，都能上演精彩的高爾夫球賽！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/105232287/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F105232287%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=03b7212a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Lady M<br />\n餐廳<br />\nLady M<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\nLady M 機場店是香港第五間分店，旅客在登機前不但可以在堂食區域內享用一系列件裝蛋糕及飲品，更可以將機場店獨家供應的冷凍千層蛋糕攜帶上機。每個預先冷凍的蛋糕以獨立密封包裝，並隨蛋糕附送保溫袋及適量乾冰，不論是長途或短途的旅程也適合攜帶，解凍後即可隨時享用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/105207911/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F105207911%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=ccfe70c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Beef &amp; Liberty - Bacon Cheese<br />\n餐廳, 漢堡<br />\nBeef &amp; Liberty（香港國際機場）<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\nBeef &amp; Liberty 於香港國際機場的分店設100個坐位，為旅途匆匆的你送上經典的漢堡以及其他招牌美食，仲有多款特式本地手工啤酒，一於食飽飽先出發上機﹗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/103956704/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F103956704%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=629c5679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Hong Kong International Airport Plaza Premium Lounge<br />\n健康及美容<br />\n香港國際機場環亞機場貴賓室<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\n環亞機場貴賓室設備完善，設有私人休息間、淋浴間、互聯網工作區，等候上機的時候，可以來補眠放鬆。貴賓室供應一系列餐飲，大家要試試招牌港式魚蛋片頭湯河和自製 XO 醬！環亞機場貴賓室24小時開放，首3小時收費$880。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/103969801/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F103969801%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=da0c2897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Cathay airplane<br />\n景點, 觀光<br />\n香港機場展望台<br />\n赤鱲角<br />\n航空探知館連接着機場展望台，讓你360&deg;欣賞機場各個角落，還有飛機升降的過程。巨型露天平台上的景觀相當動人，付入場費$15都是值得的，飛機迷或是攝影發燒友，不要錯過這裏的景致！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.timeout.com/images/103968992/750/562/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.timeout.com%2Fimages%2F103968992%2F750%2F562%2Fimage.jpg&h=5c10d90c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKee Wah wife cake<br />\n選購手信<br />\n把香港味道帶回家吧！你可以在機場買到各種食品、香港主題的禮品當手信，像奇華餅家的老婆餅（如圖）和蛋卷都是優質之選。此外，記得到香港‧設計廊看看，裏面的獨特產品全是本土出品。"},{"pid":"84df2a1a79f3dd14489847be0a132a57cba563a8","tid":1433601,"uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"【親子好去處】機場2號客運大樓 童夢城通識學園<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWN19h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWN19h.jpg&h=7c1a2ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98sgZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98sgZ8.jpg&h=1cdda43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ba3cd52e468c702f70c123b481f9aa89ca82fd","tid":1433601,"uid":136987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ed7146f4b90b7d6c49b93882830939d26d7314","tid":1433601,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01ba3cd52e468c702f70c123b481f9aa89ca82fd","tid":1433601,"uid":136987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}